Silence::

She felt the axe drop on the back of her neck. In a slightly unsteady
tone, " uh, yes sir. I will be there presently." Great, now I am to
get the punishment I so rishly deserve for my insulence earlier to a
superior officer, he may be a decepticreep, but he's still my
superior, she thought as she made her way to his office. If her sence
of honor wasn't at stake, she'd fly away. Getting a 'tongue lashing'
wasn't her idea of fun, but she deserved it.  She walked over and
knocked on the door to his office. "I am here sir."
